OL,3,C'Our shop staff deserve no less': Call
OL,4,Cfor NI shop assault law
OL,6,FThere have been calls for specific
OL,7,Flaws in Northern Ireland for attacks
OL,8,Fon shop workers.
OL,10,FIt comes after Prime Minister Rishi
OL,11,FSunak announced that his government
OL,12,Fwill be amending its Criminal Justice
OL,13,FBill to bring in the new offence,
OL,14,Fwhich will only apply in England and
OL,15,FWales
