OL,3,C'Our shop staff deserve no less': Call
OL,4,Cfor NI shop assault law
OL,6,FHe said: "I am sending a message to
OL,7,Fthose criminals ` whether they are
OL,8,Fserious organised criminal gangs,
OL,9,Frepeat offenders or opportunistic
OL,10,Fthieves ` who think they can get away
OL,11,Fwith stealing from these local
OL,12,Fbusinesses or abusing shopworkers,
OL,13,Fenough is enough.J"Our local shops are
OL,14,Fthe lifeblood of our communities, and
OL,15,Fthey must be free to trade without the
OL,16,Fthreat of crime or abuse."
