OL,3,C'Our shop staff deserve no less': Call
OL,4,Cfor NI shop assault law
OL,6,FThe new offence will carry a maximum
OL,7,Fsentence of six months' imprisonment
OL,8,For an unlimited fine, the same
OL,9,Fsentence for the existing offence of
OL,10,Fcommon assault.JRepeat offenders could
OL,11,Falso be forced to wear an electronic
OL,12,Ftag, as could consistent shoplifters,
OL,13,Funder amendments to the Bill currently
OL,14,Fmaking its way through Parliament.
OL,15,FRetail NI has called for Northern
OL,16,FIreland to be included in the new law.
OL,17,FRetail NI Chief Executive Glyn Roberts
OL,18,Fsaid: "This is a welcome announcement
OL,19,Fby the Prime Minister given the huge
OL,20,Fincrease in the physical and verbal
OL,21,Fabuse of shop workers in England and
OL,22,FWales.
