OL,3,C'Our shop staff deserve no less': Call
OL,4,Cfor NI shop assault law
OL,6,F"Northern Ireland is now the only part
OL,7,Fof the UK not to have such laws to
OL,8,Fdeter criminals and to protect shop
OL,9,Fstaff.
OL,11,F"In two weeks Retail NI will be
OL,12,Flaunching a comprehensive report on
OL,13,Fthe experiences of our members
OL,14,Frelating to business crime. It will
OL,15,Falso outline what the Department of
OL,16,FJustice and PSNI need to do to tackle
OL,17,Fit.
OL,19,F"Top of our list is for this law to
OL,20,Finclude Northern Ireland.
