OL,3,C'Our shop staff deserve no less': Call
OL,4,Cfor NI shop assault law
OL,6,F"Our shop staff deserve no less."
OL,7,FJustice minister Naomi Long says she's
OL,8,Fconsidering introducing further legal
OL,9,Fprotections for shop workers.
OL,11,FShe added: "I condemn all abuse and
OL,12,Fviolence directed at any frontline
OL,13,Fworkers.
OL,15,F"No-one should face mistreatment
OL,16,Fwhilst doing their job and serving the
OL,17,Fpublic and such attacks are wholly
OL,18,Funacceptable and must not be tolerated.
